REQUIREMENTS:
- Annotate every beat listed above, exactly once, keyed by its full beat id.
- Assign exactly one scene_type (scene, sequel, micro_beat) AND one narration_scope
  (limited, wide) to each.
- Assign every limited beat a viewpoint from the character ids above; give every
  wide beat viewpoint "". Set interlude true only for beats of the scheme's named
  deviant register.
